# AIR-327: Membership Benefit correctly applies only to configured Kids Meal modifiers

## Summary
Test completed. Membership benefit is now correctly applied only to configured Kids Meal entrée modifiers in POS.

## Environment
- Version: v0.25.2  
- Env: Staging (Admin & POS)  
- Admin URL: https://staging.airtopiapark.com/admin/product/69b9c4908a95246f37b9e7ec  
- POS URL: https://staging.airtopiapark.com/pos/order/create  

## Test Result
✅ Passed

## Preconditions
- Membership benefit (Elite Founder) is configured:
  - Product: Kids Meal  
  - Modifiers: Nachos, French Fries, Applesauce  

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Open POS → Create Order  
2. Add Kids Meal  
3. Select entrée = Hot Dog (not included in configured modifiers)  
4. Apply membership (Elite Founder)  

## Expected Result
Discount should NOT be applied when selected entrée is not included in the configured modifier list.

## Actual Result
Discount is NOT applied when entrée (Hot Dog) is not part of the configured modifiers.  
Discount is applied correctly only for configured modifiers (Nachos, French Fries, Applesauce).

